{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/change-the-color-of-text","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-css","demoType":null,"title":"Promeni Boju Teksta","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada promenimo boju dela naseg teksta.</p>\n<p>To mozemo uraditi promenom <code>style</code> vrednosti vaseg <code>h2</code> elementa.</p>\n<p>Svojstvo koje kontrolise boju teksta elementa je <code>color</code>.</p>\n<p>Ovako mozete postaviti boju teksta vaseg <code>h2</code> elementa na plavu:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;h2 style=\"color: blue;\">CatPhotoApp&#x3C;/h2>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Zapamtite da je dobra praksa da se inline <code>style</code> deklaracije zavrsavaju sa <code>;</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aedf08803","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Promenite stil svog <code>h2</code> elementa tako da boja teksta bude crvena.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cRkVmSm","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16775,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/change-the-color-of-text"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<h2>CatPhotoApp</h2>\n<main>\n  <p>Click here to view more <a href=\"#\">cat photos</a>.</p>\n\n  <a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n\n  <div>\n    <p>Things cats love:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>catnip</li>\n      <li>laser pointers</li>\n      <li>lasagna</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\n    <ol>\n      <li>flea treatment</li>\n      <li>thunder</li>\n      <li>other cats</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n\n  <form 